import { Component, OnInit } from "@angular/core"; @Component({ selector: "app-cart", templateUrl: "./cart.component.html", styleUrls: ["./cart.component.scss"], }) export class CartComponent implements OnInit { public counter: number = 1; constructor() {} ngOnInit() {} public increment() { this.counter += 1; } public decrement() { if (this.counter > 1) { this.counter -= 1; } } }
